{"tid":669333,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"比KFC個弱智員工搞到唔敢食野","createTime":"2018-05-18T11:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T12:21:00.000Z","uid":73529,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cb623d3a18828c970852799db0625f20188621c6","tid":669333,"uid":73529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T11:06:11.000Z","msg":"話說頭先我放工去買野食<br />\n睇到kfc出左咩5重盒咪去食<br />\n比完錢啦，正正常常去等餐<br />\n汁餐個個人就係個弱智員工（我唔知係咪真弱智啦）<br />\n起度叫人拎餐個時大聲9叫<br />\n咁都算啦，我都係叫外賣拎完就走姐<br />\n點知佢一見到我張單就9笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆街我心諗咩9<br />\n過左一陣佢冇再笑<br />\n到佢叫我去拎餐<br />\n一拎起個下又即刻9笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家返到屋企都唔敢食<br />\n唔知係咪d跌左落地嘅雞<br />\n比個弱智見到所以先識笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c180ccd165b36c76a41f479621a9030210889b4","tid":669333,"uid":2419,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T11:07:19.000Z","msg":"佢見到同類所以開心姐"},{"pid":"72f6682b278c069b6161e11b3c601df0f567bd39","tid":669333,"uid":65587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T11:08:15.000Z","msg":"佢終於見到有人弱智過佢 字都唔撚識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd7a5c97575c218019339cd01318c838397a295","tid":669333,"uid":106506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T11:08:43.000Z","msg":"打咗飛機射咗落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37928df3cbdd3dd6d510dfafec65c36a2654856","tid":669333,"uid":47029,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T11:10:34.000Z","msg":"kfc請埋d人係有問題，之前屋企樓下有個精神病既女人，永遠撞到佢都係對住空氣鬧人，之後有次係海港城kfc撞到佢做，見佢同客講野又正正常常咁仲諗住佢終於好返，點知過幾日又撞到佢係樓下係咁鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65142cdc99bd746ce717902374cfb78a8f3229ee","tid":66